Cell["\<\
FindShell[g, c, r] returns one metric shell { v : d(c, v) == r } around c. \
Returns a List of unary InfraShell[{set}] wrappers; n / UpTo[n] / All control \
multiplicity. Option Method (\"Metric\" (default) | \"Separating\" | \
\"Embedding\").\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"2b3ce258-fb5b-474d-9c80-314bfa52a44c"],

